      <title>前外汇主管称干预是日元过度疲软的选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/former-fx-chief-says-intervention-an-option-for-overly-weak-yen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本前货币主管表示，干预是解决日元过度疲软问题的选择之一，他在美国通胀数据公布之前发表讲话，该数据可能会推动日元突破市场参与者密切关注的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/former-fx-chief-says-intervention-an-option-for-overly-weak-yen</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:16:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于持续的风险，明年欧洲天然气价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/european-gas-prices-through-next-year-rise-on-persistent-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲天然气小幅走高，由于供应风险（包括来自俄罗斯的剩余流量）持续存在不确定性，预计明年冬季燃料价格将更加昂贵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/european-gas-prices-through-next-year-rise-on-persistent-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:09:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
